#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.sinh.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.sinh"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sinh.sinh:1 of
msgid "Hyperbolic sine, element-wise."
msgstr "双曲正弦，逐元素计算。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sinh.sinh:3 of
msgid ""
"Equivalent to ``1/2 * (mt.exp(x) - mt.exp(-x))`` or ``-1j * "
"mt.sin(1j*x)``."
msgstr "等价于 ``1/2 * (mt.exp(x) - mt.exp(-x))`` 或 ``-1j * mt.sin(1j*x)``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sinh.sinh of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sinh.sinh:6 of
msgid "Input tensor."
msgstr "输入张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sinh.sinh:8 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供了该参数，则其形状必须可以广播到输入形状。"
"如果未提供或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（仅能作为关键字参数）"
"的长度必须等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sinh.sinh:13 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的原值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sinh.sinh of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sinh.sinh:18 of
msgid "**y** -- The corresponding hyperbolic sine values."
msgstr "**y** -- 对应的双曲正弦值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sinh.sinh of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sinh.sinh:22 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sinh.sinh:23 of
msgid ""
"If `out` is provided, the function writes the result into it, and returns"
" a reference to `out`.  (See Examples)"
msgstr ""
"如果提供了 `out`，函数会将结果写入其中，并返回对 `out` 的引用。（参见示例"
"）"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sinh.sinh:27 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.sinh.sinh:28 of
msgid ""
"M. Abramowitz and I. A. Stegun, Handbook of Mathematical Functions. New "
"York, NY: Dover, 1972, pg. 83."
msgstr ""
"M. Abramowitz 和 I. A. Stegun，《数学函数手册》。纽约：Dover，1972年，第"
"83页。"

